<h3>Readability</h3>
<p>Sa11y's readability feature is based on <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flesch%E2%80%93Kincaid_readability_tests#Flesch_reading_ease">Flesch reading-ease test (Wikipedia)</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lix_(readability_test)">Lix (Wikipedia).</a> The Flesch reading-ease formula has been adapted to also support Dutch, Italian, French, German, and Spanish. Lix formula supports Danish, Finnish, Norwegian (BokmÃ¥l & Nynorsk), and Swedish.</p>

